	Strong computer science background (knowledge of machine learning is a plu=
s)
	Strong knowledge of applied math (linear algebra, signal processing, Fouri=
er analysis, polynomial expansions)
	Strong oral, written and interpersonal communication skills (working langu=
age: English =E2=80=93 knowing French is a plus)
	Good knowledge of C++
	Fair knowledge of parallel computing frameworks (threading libraries and G=
PU)
